Parametric Bootstrap Standard Errors

Source: R/simAutoReg-p-boot-se.R
PBootSE.Rd

Parametric Bootstrap Standard Errors

Usage

PBootSE(x)

Arguments

x

Numeric matrix. Output of PBootVAROLS().

Value

A matrix of standard error.

See also

Other Simulation of Autoregressive Data Functions: FitVARLassoSearch(), FitVARLasso(), FitVAROLS(), LambdaSeq(), OrigScale(), PBootCI(), PBootVARLasso(), PBootVAROLS(), SearchVARLasso(), SelectVARLasso(), SimAR(), SimMVN(), SimVARZIP(), SimVAR(), SimVariance(), StdMat(), YX()

Author

Ivan Jacob Agaloos Pesigan
